						<summary>

						<p>It records the gift of money (<hi rend="italic">achchu</hi>) for twilight lamp at the temple of Piṇakaṟukkum-nāyanār at Maliyaḍikkuṟichchi, which was a southern hamlet of Śrī Parāntaka-chaturvēdimaṅgalam a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> in Āri-nādu by one Arasubālaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kulasēkharappallavaraiyan, an official (<hi rend="italic">karātchi</hi>) of the temple.</p>						

